responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "5C35099642F719EE73DB13AAD51FD01B", "By the Seven! It\'s power was the power of possession. It must have consumed Prince Dagon whole and used his body to spread its evil wrath. Not even in the hands of benevolence could the force be harnessed for good. This must be given to the Scholars Academy of Verra. I\'m sure the mages will find some way to harness or hide the artifact of evil. Verra is in your debt.")
